{"tid":208370,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"住屯門元朗元水圍既你地，CV敢唔敢報真地址?","createTime":"2017-04-19T13:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T13:08:05.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"717ac939772740e363686fce65c25de0e5738688","tid":208370,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港好多顧主都歧視住屯/元/天既人<br />\n見你住呢d地方就覺得你低賤過其他人<br />\n連叫你來見工都唔見<br />\n<br />\n我唔係鳩吹<br />\n我試過有段時間求職<br />\n報住屯門無乜人叫我去見工<br />\n一報住九龍就好多面試邀請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉 下次見工都係繼續報住九龍算"},{"pid":"151a29c34dd345f0bb04cbc1043206fe53638ce6","tid":208370,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"冇人住屯元天? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890183a34bac7eea820b52369c05408e3a166d06","tid":208370,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"CV從來唔會落自己地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇必要.."},{"pid":"c3790754c86a28656306f585f771df83fa839f06","tid":208370,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"有朋友住屯門失業左半年，後尾地址報service apartment冇耐有幾個offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7b63a9e286755b1f49c1013c82b3004ad59417","tid":208370,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e765331b4c0d880b9b238e0663b21d7ae850f9de","tid":208370,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c6482d1fd6eb577fea5fa82397cb5a9206d5e0b4","tid":208370,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"首先CV唔會報地址咁ON9先<br />\n其次.....我係僱主唔會撚理你住邊<br />\n你自己搵工先會考慮咁遠反唔反到既問題呀話"},{"pid":"84395eec95feacce5775a63c497d07e88a1eefea","tid":208370,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"大陸居民入城工作手續麻煩"},{"pid":"f4c72c52acbe62d2876607aea5da870be7df206d","tid":208370,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先CV唔會報地址咁ON9先<br />\n其次.....我係僱主唔會撚理你住邊<br />\n你自己搵工先會考慮咁遠反唔反到既問題呀話</blockquote><br />\n留地址主要係用黎通訊 取錄通知書都要寄掛? 不過應該間間公司做法唔同<br />\n<br />\n搵工方面唔係每間公司都有特定工作地點<br />\n好多時會睇你住邊派你去station<br />\n如果你係新界西但果頭又冇空缺咪bye鳩bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e061f867e9c2b90ab1c876ceb42049ae33b91c","tid":208370,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"見工問到先會講<br />\n講親都以為你住火星 日日都番唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b7237fa1a322aa53bd855950e5fc4e531af68b","tid":208370,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"CV駛柒報地址,多餘"},{"pid":"f0b3d973509259804040fb9076792c94b812fd04","tid":208370,"uid":105604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"學到野<br />\n即刻del佐個地址<br />\n以前濕尻學校教寫cv要寫地址"},{"pid":"189b6e2592fda30bdffc8b0a2189cfef247bb76f","tid":208370,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:10:54.000Z","msg":"騎牛出入好失禮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5865d30ba7e4eec29524326e469fdb6b3a0008","tid":208370,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"有畢架山同天水圍地址可以報<br />\n<br />\n填畢架山個份cv, send親都有回覆"},{"pid":"b5c242fe3c62fa8e15b350fe755b64120a2efd49","tid":208370,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友住屯門失業左半年，後尾地址報service apartment冇耐有幾個offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor